      Framework :: Play Framework (support RESTFULL architecture )
      DataBase :: MongoDB [NOSQL]

       To run the project :: ./activator run
        
        Minimum Requirememt :: 
                         MongDB[please update the ip add and port for mongo server in in                           
                         /conf/DBconfig.properties],
                         Java 8 

    API ::
   GET                /list                      controllers.ApplicationController.getAll()
   GET                /                          controllers.ApplicationController.getMapService()   
   GET                /count                     controllers.ApplicationController.getCount()   
   GET                /search/:query  controllers.ApplicationController.getResult(query)


  For search::
             pattern is name or category = value
                                 for example http://localhost:9000/search/name=PizzaHut

All response are in JSON

